version_mismatch.zh: 当前版本 {current_version} < 要求的最低版本 {min_required_version}，请下载最新版本: {update_url}
version_mismatch.en: Current version {current_version} < required minimum version {min_required_version}, please download the latest version: {update_url}

title.zh: 此修复工具适用于WWMI生产的Mod因游戏版本更新导致失效的情况
title.en: This fix tool is applicable when the mods produced by WWMI become ineffective due to the update of the game version.

intro.zh:
修复2.8: 女漂
* 千咲光照贴图hash更新(更新于11/21)
* 新增千咲强化e受伤表现移除(需更新至2.8.1)
* 黑海岸NPC身体贴图hash更新

修复2.7: 赞妮 芙露德莉斯
修复2.6: 修复所有角色的贴图错误
* 修复下列武器的贴图错误: 奇幻变奏 漪澜浮录 赫奕流明 千古洑流 停驻之烟 裁春 血誓盟约 擎渊怒涛 东落 浩境粼光 时和岁稔 凋亡频率 心之锚
* 修复露帕NPC 露帕尾巴 赞妮盾牌 珂莱塔水晶头发 芙露德莉丝的剑 滑翔翼(默认) 翱翔翼(默认) 菲比法杖 白芷宠物 黑海岸NPC身体 阿布
* 添加奥古斯塔的受伤表现移除
* 补充红椿和丹瑾及安可遗漏的头发光照贴图和折枝的眼睛贴图hash
* 修复替换女角色的编队肖像hash
* 新增: 补充遗漏的散华脸部贴图hash
intro.en:
Fix 2.8: RoverFemale
* Updated hash of Chisa's lightmap (Updated on 11/21)
* Added removal of Chisa's enhanced E skill wounded_effect (requires update to version 2.8.1)
* Updated hash of BlackshoreNPC_Body diffusemap

Fix 2.7: Zani Flurdelys
Fix 2.6: Fixed texture errors for all characters
* Fixed texture errors for the following weapons: Variation CosmicRipples BlazingBrilliance EmeraldOfGenesis StaticMist RedSpring Bloodpact'sPledge 
AbyssSurges HeliosCleaver LustrousRazor AgesOfHarvest WaningRedshift SomnoireAnchor
* Fixed texture errors for LupaNpc LupaTail Zani_Shield CarlottaHairCrystal FleurdelysSword Glider(normal) Flight(normal) PhoebeWand BaizhiPet BlackShoreNPCBody Abby
* Added the removal of the Wounded Effect of Augusta
* Added the missing hair hash for hair lightMap of RedCamellya and Danjin and Encore, as well as the missing eye texture hash for Zhezhi.
* Replace the team portrait hash of the female characters
* New: Added the missing face texture hash of the Sanhua

intro_note.zh: 将WWMI更新至0.9.6以修复损坏的面部(和肩部)动画
intro_note.en: Update WWMI to version 0.9.6 to fix the broken facial (and shoulder) animations.

compatibility_note.zh: 注：wwmi 0.6x版本的旧Mod在WWMI 070版本之后需开启兼容模式才能加载. 从WWMI076开始默认关闭了兼容模式. 开启方式: 游戏内 Alt + F12. 显示 Compatibility Mode: Enabled
compatibility_note.en: Note: The old mods of the WWMI 0.6x version need to have the compatibility mode enabled to be loaded after the WWMI 070 version. Starting from WWMI 076, the compatibility mode is turned off by default. The way to enable it is: press Alt + F12 in the game. It should display 'Compatibility Mode: Enabled'.

graphics_setting_note.zh: 游戏从2.0版本开始不同画面预设的Hash值可能不同，这可能导致Mod贴图错误，请将图形质量预设调整至均衡/画质优先
graphics_setting_note.en: Starting from version 2.0, different graphics presets may have different hash values, which may cause mod texture errors. Please set the graphics quality preset to Balanced/Quality.

texture_override_note.zh: 游戏2.1版本已经在设置添加了受伤表现开关，此工具仍提供战损修复功能，建议坎特蕾拉启用，除此目前2.6以前的角色暂不建议启用此选项
texture_override_note.en: In game 2.1 version, 'Wounded Effect' has been added to the settings, this tool still provides injured texture hash fix, It is recommended to enable this option for Cantarella. However, for characters prior to version 2.6, it is not recommended to enable this option.

texture_override_prompt.zh: 是否移除受伤表现？ （默认否）:

rabbit_fx_stable_texture_note.zh: 使用RabbitFX的'Stable texture'功能移除战损/湿身(目前仅坎特蕾拉)，需安装RabbitFX_v65
rabbit_fx_stable_texture_note.en: To remove the injured/wet of Characters with RabbitFX's 'Stable texture' feature(currently only Cantarella), RabbitFX_v65 is required

found_old_mod.zh: 发现旧版Mod(wwmi 0.6x)，正在尝试修复...
found_old_mod.en: Found old mod (wwmi 0.6x), trying to fix...

injured_hash_replace_note.en: Character {character} has injured texture hash {original_hash} -> section {section_header}

injured_hash_replace_warning.zh: 文件 {file_path} 中没有找到合适的位置插入战损修复节，请手动检查
injured_hash_replace_warning.en: No suitable position found for injured texture hash replacement in file {file_path}, please check manually

process_file_done.zh: 已完成对文件 {file_path} 的处理

no_need_fix.zh: 未匹配到修复，跳过备份与处理
no_need_fix.en: No need to fix, skip backup and processing

process_file_error.zh: 处理文件 {file_path} 时出现异常: {exception}

process_folder_done.zh: 共处理了 {success_count} 个文件，跳过 {failure_count} 个文件

input_folder_prompt.zh: 请输入包含Mod文件的文件夹路径（直接回车则从当前目录开始）:
input_folder_prompt.en: Please enter the folder path containing mod files (press Enter to use current directory):

start_processing.zh: 开始处理文件夹 {mod_folder_path} 下的Mod ini文件
start_processing.en: Start processing mod ini files in folder {mod_folder_path}

all_done.zh: 所有文件处理完成，按回车键关闭窗口...
all_done.en: All files processed, press Enter to exit...

error_prompt.zh: 程序出现异常，请查看上述错误信息，按任意键关闭窗口...
error_prompt.en: An error occurred. Please check the error message above and press any key to exit...

aero_rover_female_eyes_prompt.zh: 是否修复女漂-风主形态满共鸣能量时眼睛异常？确保你的mod存在此问题，否则不要开启! （默认否）:
aero_rover_female_eyes_prompt.en: Fix eyes of female aero-rover when it has full charge? Make sure your mod has the problem, otherwise don't enable it! (default no):

aero_rover_female_eyes_fixed.zh: 女漂-风主形态满共鸣能量时眼睛已修复
aero_rover_female_eyes_fixed.en: Female aero-rover eyes fixed when it has full charge

path_not_a_directory.zh: 路径 {path} 不是一个有效的目录
path_not_a_directory.en: Path {path} is not a valid directory

permission_check_remove_failed.zh: 无法删除临时权限检查文件 {path}，请手动删除。错误: {error}
permission_check_remove_failed.en: Failed to remove temporary permission check file {path}, please remove it manually. Error: {error}

permission_check_create_failed.zh: 在 {path} 创建文件失败，请检查写权限。错误: {error}
permission_check_create_failed.en: Failed to create file in {path}, please check write permissions. Error: {error}

admin_prompt_suggestion.zh: 建议以管理员身份重新运行此程序以获取足够的权限。
admin_prompt_suggestion.en: It is recommended to re-run this program as an administrator to get sufficient permissions.

traversal_error.zh: 遍历目录时出错: {path}, 错误: {error}
